    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120160/extras/152659ea8471a221274a1d470c49f4a2.poster.avif?t=1743627052\" width=564 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120160/extras/152659ea8471a221274a1d470c49f4a2.webm?t=1743627052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120160/extras/152659ea8471a221274a1d470c49f4a2.mp4?t=1743627052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tres</strong> is a cards-based game where you, with another player, have to compete againt each other to see who is the first to put on the table all of their cards. The first player to clear their deck 3 times wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120160/extras/628c1d95d8ad8b4ab05d2a3502143483.poster.avif?t=1743627052\" width=564 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120160/extras/628c1d95d8ad8b4ab05d2a3502143483.webm?t=1743627052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120160/extras/628c1d95d8ad8b4ab05d2a3502143483.mp4?t=1743627052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It really isn't, every card has it's pros and cons, take this example; you can swap your deck with your opponent, but you never know what they have. The game has 50+ cards, and a lot of them have a special function, it could be a draw card, a block card, or even a <strong>KNIFE</strong>?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclaimer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to play this game, it's highly recommended to play it with a friend. Since you are forced to play in a game being two players.</p>",
